    <item>
      <title>Recipe using C&#43;&#43; standard library ingredients</title>
      <link>https://rajatbajpai.com/post/api_design_with_performance/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://rajatbajpai.com/post/api_design_with_performance/</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Designing a good utility is a complex task because of the number of people going to use it. I believe any utility has three primary purposes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It must give the correct results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It should be easy to use.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;It should have adequate performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, I will discuss the third point: performance. The performance of a utility is paramount. If the utility is used in several places, then these degradations will add up to massive degradation. Thus, while designing a utility, we should be careful and think about the various approaches. We should think about the various tradeoffs each approach has. One approach might not be best for all situations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;rsquo;s jump right into the example. Suppose we need to design an API that will return if an element exists in top N elements in a sequence. For example, you have a sequence (5, 4, 3, 2, 1), and you need to check if 3 exists in the top 3 elements. In this case, the answer will be Yes. I have discussed three approaches to design this API.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First, the straightforward approach will be to sort the whole array and check if an element exists in the top N elements. This approach is functionally correct and will be fine if we have small sequences. However, this approach will not provide adequate performance for large sequences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cpp&#34; data-lang=&#34;cpp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;bool&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;is_top_n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sort&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;])&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Second, we can improve on the first approach. Instead of sorting the whole sequence, we can partially sort N elements of the sequence. That&amp;rsquo;s shown in the code below. Interestingly, initially, I thought this approach is better than the first approach. I mean it should be because, in the first approach, we are sorting the whole sequence, while in this approach, we are sorting the top N elements. However, performance numbers don&amp;rsquo;t agree with me. See the performance numbers at the end of the post. I believe this is happening because of the different algorithms used in the &lt;code&gt;std::sort&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;std::partial_sort&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cpp&#34; data-lang=&#34;cpp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;bool&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;is_top_n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;partial_sort&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;])&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Third, instead of sorting the whole sequence or partial sequence, we can use &lt;code&gt;std::nth_element&lt;/code&gt; to put boundary elements of the sequence in their correct position. As expected, this approach is far better than the above two approaches. You can take a look at the performance numbers at the end to see for yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cpp&#34; data-lang=&#34;cpp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;bool&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;is_top_n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;nth_element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;])&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;nth_element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;elem&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sequences&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;])&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nb&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://rajatbajpai.com/img/performance_pos.png&#34; alt=&#34;performance numbers&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That&amp;rsquo;s it, we designed a utility and improved its initial design and saw that sometimes what we think will improve the performance doesn&amp;rsquo;t do so. Thus, when you are designing for performance, please benchmark your different approaches. That&amp;rsquo;s the only way to be sure.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Know your tools: std::nth_element</title>
      <link>https://rajatbajpai.com/post/nth_element/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Aug 2021 22:27:12 +0530</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://rajatbajpai.com/post/nth_element/</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;All seasoned C++ developers are aware of the standard library and all the algorithms it provides. Today, I will discuss one such algorithm that is more efficient in a large dataset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Without further ado, let&amp;rsquo;s jump right into the problem statement. Let&amp;rsquo;s suppose we are tasked to build an API that returns the medium of the distribution. I will discuss two approaches to design the API.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First, we can use &lt;code&gt;std::sort&lt;/code&gt; to sort the whole distribution and pick the middle two elements if we have even numbers in the distribution and the middle element if we have odd numbers in the distribution. While this approach is functionally correct; however, think about the scenario when we have millions of numbers in the distribution. We will be sorting the whole distribution even though we require only the middle elements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cpp&#34; data-lang=&#34;cpp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;median&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;();&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;sort&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;])&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;];&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;
We can optimize the first approach by sorting distribution in such a way that middle elements are in their correct positions. In other words, middle elements will be those as if we have sorted the whole distribution. This is exactly what we are doing in the second approach using &lt;code&gt;std::nth_element&lt;/code&gt;. The benefit of the second approach is that we don&amp;rsquo;t have to sort the whole distribution upfront.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cpp&#34; data-lang=&#34;cpp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;algorithm&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;median&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;kt&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;();&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;firstMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;nth_element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;firstMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;len&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;!=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;firstMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;secondMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;firstMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;nth_element&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;secondMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;numbers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;firstMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;secondMiddleElementItr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;mi&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s evident from the above discussion that we can devise neat APIs using the standard library algorithms.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Curious case of std::optional utility</title>
      <link>https://rajatbajpai.com/post/optional/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://rajatbajpai.com/post/optional/</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In 2017, C++ standard introduced &lt;code&gt;std::optional&lt;/code&gt; utility to represent nullable types. In this post, I will try to explain the logical use case for &lt;code&gt;std::optional&lt;/code&gt; with the help of a real example (I mean sort of!).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I work on the SystemVerilog compiler at Cadence. The SystemVerilog language provides some system utilities, and they are called &lt;em&gt;System Function Call&lt;/em&gt; expressions. Interestingly, these utilities can have empty parameters. In other words, parameters of a &lt;em&gt;System Function Call&lt;/em&gt; expressions are optional (tada!). All the SystemVerilog stuff aside, we can represent this expression in Abstract Syntax Tree (AST). In AST, we can have two fields: name and vector of actual parameters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Before we jump to AST design using &lt;code&gt;std::optional&lt;/code&gt;, I will show you how I would have done it without the &lt;code&gt;std::optional&lt;/code&gt;. The first example is using &lt;code&gt;std::nullptr&lt;/code&gt; to represent empty parameters. Furthermore, it is using pointers to use &lt;code&gt;std::nullptr&lt;/code&gt; as a sentinel value to represent empty parameters. If we want to store value instead of pointers, then we need to devise a sentinel value to represent empty parameter. Honestly, I don&amp;rsquo;t think it is a bad design to use &lt;code&gt;std::nullptr&lt;/code&gt; for an empty parameter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cpp&#34; data-lang=&#34;cpp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;iostream&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;memory&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;string_view&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nc&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{};&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nc&#34;&gt;SystemFunctionCallAST&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// Constructors...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;SystemFunctionCallAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;string_view&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
                        &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;unique_ptr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;reserve&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;size&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;());&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nl&#34;&gt;arg&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;push_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;move&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;arg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;));&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;string_view&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;unique_ptr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// ... other members
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;};&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;createDisplaySystemFunctionCall&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;unique_ptr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;emplace_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;make_unique&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;());&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;emplace_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;nullptr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;emplace_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;nullptr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;emplace_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;make_unique&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;());&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;SystemFunctionCallAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;$display&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;
In contrast, the second example is using &lt;code&gt;std::optional&lt;/code&gt; to represent parameters. The &lt;code&gt;std::optional&lt;/code&gt; utility provides a special type to represent the null value (&lt;code&gt;std::nullopt&lt;/code&gt;); thus, we don&amp;rsquo;t need to devise a new sentinel for this purpose.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cpp&#34; data-lang=&#34;cpp&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;iostream&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;optional&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;string_view&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cpf&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;vector&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cp&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nc&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{};&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nc&#34;&gt;SystemFunctionCallAST&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// Constructors
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;SystemFunctionCallAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;string_view&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;optional&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;),&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{}&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// ....
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// Observers...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArguments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;noexcept&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;private&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;string_view&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;name_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;optional&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;actualArgs_&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;// ... other members
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;};&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;auto&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;nf&#34;&gt;createDisplaySystemFunctionCall&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;vector&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;optional&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;emplace_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;ExpressionAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;());&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;emplace_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;nullopt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;emplace_back&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;std&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;nullopt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;span class=&#34;k&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;SystemFunctionCallAST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;$display&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;n&#34;&gt;args&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;In summary, I believe &lt;code&gt;std::optional&lt;/code&gt; offers some logical use cases where we can use it while developing software applications using C++. However, we might need to think of new ways to design our applications.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
